OL,3,CMore than '30,000 lives saved' thanks
OL,4,Cto suicide prevention project
OL,6,FA suicide prevention charity set up by
OL,7,Fa woman whose father took his own life
OL,8,Fhas made more than 30,000 life saving
OL,9,Finterventions since it started five
OL,10,Fyears ago.
OL,12,FJessica Gallier's father Martin took
OL,13,Fhis own life seven years ago. She set
OL,14,Fup two years after his death, so that
OL,15,Fpeople who are struggling can get help.
