OL,3,CMore than '30,000 lives saved' thanks
OL,4,Cto suicide prevention project
OL,6,FThe charity has grown rapidly since
OL,7,Fits formation, as many people have
OL,8,Fstruggled with their mental health
OL,9,Famid pandemic isolation and the
OL,10,Ffinancial pain of the cost-of-living
OL,11,Fcrisis.
OL,13,FThe centre Jessica opened in New Ferry
OL,14,Fon the Wirral was groundbreaking and
OL,15,Fwas the only place offering non
OL,16,Fclinical suicide intervention on the
OL,17,Fhigh street. There are no barriers to
OL,18,Faccess, criteria and no waiting lists.
