OL,3,CMore than '30,000 lives saved' thanks
OL,4,Cto suicide prevention project
OL,6,FJessica said: "It was a first of its
OL,7,Fkind and I think in my depths of grief
OL,8,Fi didn't realise how big that was.
OL,10,F"I knew it was going to be utilised,
OL,11,Fbut I had something in my ear saying
OL,12,Fthat this was going to be a waste of
OL,13,Ftime, this isn't going to work.
OL,15,F"When I look back and think what we've
OL,16,Fdone in five years. It has worked, and
OL,17,Fthe charity has saved thousands of
OL,18,Flives."
