OL,3,CMore than '30,000 lives saved' thanks
OL,4,Cto suicide prevention project
OL,6,FWhen Martin Gallier took his life at
OL,7,Fthe age of 55, it was not his first
OL,8,Fsuicide attempt.
OL,10,FAfter the inquest, Jessica said she
OL,11,Fthought there had to be a "better way
OL,12,Fof supporting people in suicidal
OL,13,Fcrisis."
OL,15,FShe decided she could keep "banging
OL,16,Fthis drum" to existing services or
OL,17,Fopen her own support charity.
OL,19,FJessica said: "It's bigger than
OL,20,Fanything I could have imagined.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
