OL,3,CMore than '30,000 lives saved' thanks
OL,4,Cto suicide prevention project
OL,6,F"Just to think that something so
OL,7,Fpainful like losing my dad to suicide
OL,8,Fand to think that there are all those
OL,9,Fpeople who are still alive today and
OL,10,Ftheir families don't have to go
OL,11,Fthrough what we've been through
OL,12,Fbecause of that."
OL,14,FSarah Armstrong is just one of the
OL,15,Fthousands whose lives have been saved
OL,16,Fby the charity.
