OL,3,CMore than '30,000 lives saved' thanks
OL,4,Cto suicide prevention project
OL,6,FHer 15-year-old brother took his own
OL,7,Flife when she was just 14. Years later
OL,8,Fshe too was contemplating suicide. She
OL,9,Fsaid: "I definitely don't think I'd be
OL,10,Falive without their support.
OL,12,F"I felt stuck in a black hole, I just
OL,13,Fexisted and had no quality of life. No
OL,14,Fenjoyment in anything.
OL,16,F"Since that period I've had another
OL,17,Fchild that would never have existed
OL,18,Fand I got married.
