OL,3,CMore than '30,000 lives saved' thanks
OL,4,Cto suicide prevention project
OL,6,F"There are huge things have happened
OL,7,Fbecause I held on and I fought. I
OL,8,Fcouldn't see the glimmer of hope in
OL,9,Fthe black hole but it did appear."
OL,11,FSarah now works at the project,
OL,12,Fhelping to save other peoples' lives.
OL,14,FJessica said: "I get asked a lot about
OL,15,Fwhat my dad would think about the
OL,16,Fproject and I still don't know the
OL,17,Fanswer.
OL,19,F"Obviously I believe he would be
OL,20,Freally proud.
