OL,6,F"Ultimately he would be watching
OL,7,Fthinking perhaps there was another way
OL,8,Fsuicide was not the option for him and
OL,9,Fperhaps he was a lot more loved than
OL,10,Fhe realised at the time."JThere are
OL,11,Fplans for three more Martin Gallier
OL,12,FProject sites to open in the North
OL,13,FWest later this year.
